			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				First, I am glad that a dissusion in a necros abilitlies is finally getting talked about.  We are often refered to the &quot;best solo class&quot; which I bebieve is true.  The problem I have is at 51+ we become an overgrown manastone.  Our dots are too slow when it comes to a raid....and the 2 dds that we do have (chill and ignite) causes the mob to become a skeleton and the groups hate that.  Correcting the size of the skeleton might work for the taller mobs...but still has no use in sebilis on the froggies.  So, I am left at 51 casting my lich series and mana-pumping the main wizard or cleric.....ohh how fun.  The lich series is the best thing a necro has and does make us very powerful soloing...but we are almost usless in high dungens.  The second issue is Screaming Terreor.  I love this spell and in a pinch I can be the mezzer of the group.  I would like to see at 51 an uprgrade given to us.  It would be st2 and last 36 seconds and could be cast on 55 and lower mobs and have the memblur effect.  This would greatly inhance our use in the dungens and raids....and not effect our solo ability.  Since at 51 and above raids are where the action is.  Now, the new spells just released are very sad for necros above 51.  We get nothing great and no insentive to go higher.  The illusion spectre is cool, but I could care less about accuiring it. The new spells for necros need to drop more often...I have yet to see an new necro spell drop in Velious.  Third, I am outraged at the thought of allowing another class to conjure a corpse.  This is the ONLY thing we have that sets us apart from the other classes.  My wife has a druid and now with the new track she can track corpses better then I can.  So, we as necros have lost that gift and money maker at low levels, and now another item will be taken away from us.  If this does ever make it out of the test relm, I hope its only to level 50 and above shadow nights.  <BR>
<BR>
Now, I would like to respond on how to improve the necros ability in a raid.  The simple answer is easy.  Make our DOTS work 10-20 persent faster in dungens only.  This would greatly affect how much damage we could help and not just be overgrown batteries.  The naysayers will look at this as making us even more powerfull, but make it a skill earned at 51+.  51 you would get 10% faster DOTS inside, and at 55 you would get 20% faster DOTS inside.  This would not effect our solo ability at younger ages, and at 50+ when groups are needed for the nice dungens, make us better and more usefull.  Some could argue that we could rock in lower dungens.  Well guess what....WE CAN ROCK IN THEM NOW!!!  I can goto guk and with my 49 pet and own upper Guk easy.  I have soloied the new crystal caverns with a pet and root only.  So nothing has changed......we just would provide better use in the groups that we need for the better dungens.  This would only effect inside use, so no-one could say that our soloing outside could be too strong.  <BR>
<BR>
Well I hope that someone from the development teams reads this, and I know I am dreaming, and would see the logic behind my words.  I have largely stoped playing my necro in large raids do to the mana battery use only.  This is too sad since I thinks necros are the best class in the game.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Thanks for the time<BR>
<BR>
Vanell Dauthifox<BR>
51 Heritic<BR>
Prexus server
				</font>
			</td>

